                    "post_content": "<p>[video width=\"1920\" height=\"1080\" mp4=\"https:\/\/life2launch-core.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/CORE-Framework-Overview.mp4\"][\/video]<\/p><p data-start=\"214\" data-end=\"377\"><strong data-start=\"214\" data-end=\"377\">CORE is a place to figure things out, build what\u2019s missing, and help design the tools you wish existed, while navigating real life alongside other young people.<\/strong><\/p><h2 data-start=\"379\" data-end=\"409\">What is Life2Launch\u2019s CORE?\u00a0\u00a0<\/h2><p data-start=\"411\" data-end=\"627\">Life2Launch\u2019s CORE is a five-month learning and co-creation experience designed to support you through the life transition you\u2019re facing right now, whether that\u2019s school, work, identity, direction, or what comes next.<\/p><p data-start=\"629\" data-end=\"804\">From <strong data-start=\"634\" data-end=\"663\">January through June 2026<\/strong>, you\u2019ll get access to life and career readiness tools, resources, and support that help you slow down, get clear, and make intentional next-step choices that fit you.<\/p><p data-start=\"806\" data-end=\"922\">CORE is not a class.<br data-start=\"826\" data-end=\"829\" \/>It\u2019s not a one-size-fits-all program.<br data-start=\"866\" data-end=\"869\" \/>It\u2019s a shared learning space built with young people that is free and accessible.<\/p><p class=\"text-base md:text-lg text-muted-foreground max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-6 animate-fade-up opacity-0 leading-relaxed\">\u00a0<\/p>",
