                            "post_content": "CORE is for young people who are in school, working, or in between and navigating a major life transition, who want space, tools, and support to figure out what\u2019s next without pressure or pretending.\r\n\r\n- Young people graduating high school or college and unsure what comes next\r\n- Students who have stepped away or dropped out and want to re-engage on their own terms\r\n- Young adults working but questioning whether this path really fits\r\n- Young people between school, jobs, or directions and exploring next steps\r\n- Creatives, builders, explorers, and non-linear thinkers looking for clarity and confidence",
