                                    "post_date_gmt": "2026-01-05 23:13:44",
                                    "post_content": "<p>CORE is for young people who are in school, working, or in between and navigating a major life transition, who want space, tools, and support to figure out what\u2019s next without pressure or pretending.<\/p><ul><li>Young people in or graduating from high school or college and unsure what comes next<\/li><li>Students who have stepped away or dropped out and want to re-engage on their own terms<\/li><li>Young adults working but questioning whether this path really fits<\/li><li>\u00a0Young people between school, jobs, or directions, and exploring next steps<\/li><li>Creatives, builders, explorers, and non-linear thinkers looking for clarity and confidence<\/li><\/ul>",
