                                    "post_date_gmt": "2026-01-05 23:13:44",
                                    "post_content": "<p>A deep dive into the Life Launching Framework\u2014understanding your Inner World, Outer World, and how Lifestyle Designing, Belonging, and Real-World Navigating work together<\/p><ul><li>Weekly short videos and activities to explore real-life topics at your own pace<\/li><li>A youth community forum where you can ask questions, share insights, and learn from peers<\/li><li>Live weekly coaching sessions with Coach D, you can join for guidance, reflection, and support<\/li><li>Creating a physical Life Launching Portfolio\u2014a collection of insights, tools, and reflections you build over time to support your next steps<\/li><\/ul><p>CORE\u00a0is the foundation of\u00a0Life2Launch, co-created with youth shaping the LaunchPad navigation platform together.<\/p>",
