                                    "post_date": "2026-01-05 23:20:36",
                                    "post_date_gmt": "2026-01-05 23:20:36",
                                    "post_content": "<p><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-720\" src=\"https:\/\/life2launch-core.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/CORE-OVERVIEW-300x169.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"169\" \/><br \/>Our Life2Launch CORE framework was built over the last five years by youth to fill a gap that didn\u2019t exist, offering a holistic way to quiet the launching chaos of life, school, and career transitions.<\/p><p>(1) UNCOVER Your Inner World<br \/>Understand your personal operating system, what drives you, how your mind and body work, and what gives your life meaning.<\/p><p>(2) DISCOVER Your Outer World Skills<br \/>Strengthen the real-world skills and system know-how you need to move through life with confidence.<\/p><p>(3) DESIGN Your Lifestyle Pathways<br \/>Make intentional choices about how you want to live, learn, work, and grow, based on what actually fits you.<\/p><p>(4) BELONG Connection &amp; Support Systems<br \/>Build connection, support, and a sense of being seen so you can show up fully and take risks without going it alone.<\/p><p>(5) NAVIGATE Real Life<br \/>Use your awareness and skills to take action, adapt to change, and keep moving forward through life transitions.<\/p>",
