                                    "post_date": "2026-01-29 01:20:31",
                                    "post_date_gmt": "2026-01-29 01:20:31",
                                    "post_content": "<p data-start=\"147\" data-end=\"239\">CORE is built to follow a natural rhythm.<br data-start=\"188\" data-end=\"191\" \/>From new moon to full moon and back to new moon.<\/p><p data-start=\"241\" data-end=\"426\">We start fresh with a new moon.<br data-start=\"272\" data-end=\"275\" \/>We build awareness as energy grows.<br data-start=\"310\" data-end=\"313\" \/>We reach clarity and insight at the full moon.<br data-start=\"359\" data-end=\"362\" \/>Then we reflect, integrate, and begin again with more intention.<\/p><p data-start=\"428\" data-end=\"565\">This cycle helps you take big ideas and meaningful moments and break them into a flow that feels true to you.<\/p><p data-start=\"567\" data-end=\"641\" data-is-last-node=\"\" data-is-only-node=\"\">As you watch this video, notice how this rhythm shows up in your own life.<\/p>",
