                                    "post_date": "2026-01-05 23:30:05",
                                    "post_date_gmt": "2026-01-05 23:30:05",
                                    "post_content": "<p>This experience is designed to meet you where you are and move at a steady, supportive pace.<br \/><br \/>Start by reviewing the CORE schedule to see how the experience unfolds over the next five months. CORE begins on a New Moon and follows a moon-inspired learning rhythm each month, grounding first, then exploring, integrating, and acting. Each new area opens about every four weeks. Once an area opens, it stays available, so you can revisit tools and resources anytime as you need them<\/p><p>CORE Areas &amp; Dates (2026)<br \/><br \/>January 18 \u2013 February 15, 2026<br \/>Uncover: Your Inner World<\/p><p>February 17 \u2013 March 17, 2026<br \/>Discover: Your Outer World Skills<\/p><p>March 18 \u2013 April 16, 2026<br \/>Design: Lifestyle &amp; Pathway Design<\/p><p>April 17 \u2013 May 15, 2026<br \/>Belong: Connection &amp; Support Systems<\/p><p>May 16 \u2013 June 14, 2026<br \/>Navigate: Action &amp; Forward Movement<\/p><ul><li>Each month focuses on one part of the life launching framework<\/li><li>You\u2019ll explore through short videos, simple activities, and reflection<\/li><li>You can join live coaching sessions and connect with peers as much or as little as you want<\/li><li>There\u2019s no \u201ccatching up\u201d\u2014this is not linear or graded<\/li><li>You\u2019ll build your own Life Launching Portfolio as you go<\/li><li>What to do first<br \/>- Look over the schedule to understand the monthly flow<br \/>- Begin with the current focus area when it opens<br \/>- Engage at your own pace, this is about progress, not pressure<\/li><\/ul><p>CORE is here to support real life, not add more stress. Use what\u2019s helpful, skip what\u2019s not, and come back as needed.<\/p>",
